      <title>托克集团今年将减少顶级交易员的股票回购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/trafigura-cuts-share-buybacks-as-new-generation-takes-over</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，托克集团今年将减少股票回购，因为利润下降与这家大宗商品交易巨头的高层换届有关。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/trafigura-cuts-share-buybacks-as-new-generation-takes-over</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 14:15:56 GMT</pubDate>
